,{"pid":"b0b6d2160d999916bbc849a5a2dee39dcbc2327e","tid":2246064,"uid":165817,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:31:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇返伊保爾喊嗰單野 原來雲加都幾偉大食哂死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係球迷噓佢 佢先喊<br />\n雲加就話係因為自己驚輸波所以換佢走<br />\n講到係自己搞喊eboue咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢話驚輸波<br />\n原來換走eboue嗰陣已經89分鐘兼領先緊<br />\n如果雲加真係見到踢得咁差驚佢累輸波 唔會補時先郁手<br />\n<br />\n班阿狗拉哂banner叫佢躝 佢一句都冇插過班球迷<br />\n仲要話係自己搞喊伊保爾<br />\n我愛爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a9ab3cc28adec94d912ce9187200272ac577f4","tid":2246064,"uid":53121,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHP73qF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHP73qF.gif&h=2fe0375f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e01aafcd730ddde0d71b57a1245ba268d048a05","tid":2246064,"uid":367153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:19:16.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48a7a58fa78d33b118b15ff6c049d2d24e95b43","tid":2246064,"uid":9171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:28:39.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578783d40c7fa6f0cddd2ce7e721b5174372afc1","tid":2246064,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:42:14.000Z","msg":"04多好"},{"pid":"e198c915f061d9c95c3a28c79a11512705dba1d8","tid":2246064,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"578783d40c7fa6f0cddd2ce7e721b5174372afc1","tid":2246064,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:42:14.000Z","msg":"04多好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T22:35:09.000Z","msg":"雲格無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81c3d1251