/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/%E6%AD%A6%E5%BA%93%E9%85%8B%E9%95%BF%E7%90%83%E5%9C%BA%E4%BA%A8%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%95%E8%B1%A1-45828678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.dreamstime.com%2Fb%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%25BA%2593%25E9%2585%258B%25E9%2595%25BF%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%259C%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A8%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%259B%2595%25E8%25B1%25A1-45828678.jpg&h=957f3490&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c682a0e68fe1d74500d93070fa355da03963d6a","tid":2246064,"uid":119729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴 = 香港<br />\n高層 = 中共<br />\n<br />\n雲加 = 港督<br />\n<br />\n佢一定頂左好多高層既壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fe07a73056d170c56614981401c36f274e0b7d","tid":2246064,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"495843a335f519d319f8c51f4b3c895721ab100c","tid":2246064,"uid":165817,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"28b733a9500440b74e3809563770f1e5fa2e56a0","tid":2246064,"uid":8636,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"Q：這些事情會讓你發夢都在想阿仙奴和比賽嗎？<br />\nA：<span class=\"red\">當然了，每天二十四小時都和球會一同呼吸，一醒來就思考下一堂訓練課，或者下場比賽要怎樣踢。</span><br />\n但現在不會了，不過我仍然支持阿仙奴，有機會就會看比賽。當你對足球有了熱情後就會至死不渝，現在我也接受了自己永遠擺脫不了這個愛好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班反雲狗仲戲謔雲爺爺教到插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等雲爺爺停止呼吸果日就係馬撚末日之時<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:21:19.000Z","msg":"其實由雲加離任開始 俾而家嗰班咁嘅濕鳩高層陰啲陰啲掌大權 已經末末地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"我地曼聯已經食左7年屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebfa958f02a731a2bd53301efaf298aef51e7b5","tid":2246064,"uid":107611,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"045f6eccf400ee9584b0802c406493b1c6976e95","tid":2246064,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"史上最佳教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3b1b55dde2276a6402158baaff540804802710","tid":2246064,"uid":94739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"無一個教練比雲爺爺付出得更多，佢係值得尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4895ad68c8b72ffc3993823e4846a879bd748a81","tid":2246064,"uid":47311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cace29872e3d5153e4653d67906713d657d4a78a","tid":2246064,"uid":147467,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"我不會這樣說，我只是覺得，讓後人擁有更多自由可能會對球會更好，我不想成為揮不去的影子去阻礙他們的工作。而從個人層面來看，完全斬斷關係做其他事情也不錯。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係屌緊廢蛇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565e0261698d25de6929d1918b18d434d25951bd","tid":2246064,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7061c0e2b810461b2b1acfaa9448f2fede572945","tid":2246064,"uid":760,"like":2,"